BRANCHES:

## dev

for developing. default branch for that reason. 
after a new feature is done/ a major bug is fixed:

- locally verify that it builds without errors or warnings
- bump version number
- re-build pkgdown site locally 
- merge into master once all the above is well

## master

keep it clean,i.e., should NEVER fail R CMD check --as-cran. 

pkgdown site in gh-pages branch should update automatically on a push to master via the `pkgdown` Github-Action.

